Package: re.jrc.ec.europa.eu
Title: PVGIS Solar Energy API Client (EU JRC)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the PVGIS API from the European Commission Joint Research Centre. Calculate PV energy output and get solar radiation data for any location. Includes LLM context injection via pvgis_context().
